thread.title: Jess Huennekens
thread.title_full: Sheenco Travel reviewed by Jess Huennekens

author: Jess Huennekens
title: Jess Huennekens
text:
We booked our Honeymoon through Sheenco Travel and we couldn't have been happier. We stayed in five different places and while one wasn't completely aware of our situation and Sheenco took care of things before we were even able to get our luggage from the car. It speaks very highly of a place that can fix a problem that quickly.
Thank you Genevieve for helping us create beautiful memories.
